      "rationale": "Three-level Richardson extrapolation performed on coarse, medium, and fine meshes (4.2 M, 11.7 M, and 31.4 M cells). GCI for the normalised hemolysis index was 2.1% between medium and fine meshes. Achieved level 3 exceeds the MRL 2 requirement of level 2."
