      "acceptanceCriteria": "Predicted relative hemolysis index RH agrees with experimental reference within ±15% across all five operating points.",
      "rationale": "RH predictions ranged from 0.71 to 0.94 against experimental values of 0.68 to 0.97. Maximum point-wise deviation was 8.7%, satisfying the ±15% acceptance criterion at all five operating conditions."
    },
    {
